📋 Subscription is in Draft status.

ID: {{subscription_id}} | Customer: {{customer_id}} | Plan: {{subscription_plan_id}}
Status: {{status}} | Payment: {{payment_status}} | Billing: {{billing_cycle}}

The subscription record is editable before activation.
An administrator can update billing cycle, plan or payment details, then Activate.

✅ Subscription is Active.

ID: {{subscription_id}} | Customer: {{customer_id}} | Plan: {{current_plan_tier}}
Status: {{status}} | Payment: {{payment_status}} | Billing: {{billing_cycle}}
Last action: {{last_action}}

Available actions: Suspend · End Date Reached · Extend Quota · Extend Quota Again · Upgrade Plan · Switch to Annual · Reset Usage Metric

⏸️ Subscription is Suspended.

ID: {{subscription_id}} | Customer: {{customer_id}}
Status: {{status}} | Payment: {{payment_status}} | Billing: {{billing_cycle}}
Last action: {{last_action}}

Temporarily disabled by an administrator. User cannot access features.

⚠️  Note: If the subscription end date passes while suspended, it transitions to Suspended + Awaiting Renewal (end date reached while suspended).

Available actions: Activate · End Date Reached (while suspended)

⏸️🔄 Suspended — Awaiting Renewal.

ID: {{subscription_id}} | Customer: {{customer_id}}
Status: {{status}} | Payment: {{payment_status}} | Billing: {{billing_cycle}}
Last action: {{last_action}}

Edge state: subscription end date passed while the subscription was Suspended.
The FSM SuspendedState only supports activate() — the admin must Activate first
to restore access. Renewal flow is not available from this state.

🔄 Subscription is Awaiting Renewal.

ID: {{subscription_id}} | Customer: {{customer_id}} | Plan: {{current_plan_tier}}
Status: {{status}} | Payment: {{payment_status}} | Billing: {{billing_cycle}}
Last action: {{last_action}}

The billing period has ended. User access is blocked.
Available actions: Renew · Downgrade Plan · Switch to Monthly · Cancel

❌ Subscription is Cancelled.

ID: {{subscription_id}} | Customer: {{customer_id}}
Status: {{status}} | Billing: {{billing_cycle}}

This subscription has been permanently cancelled and cannot be reactivated.
A new subscription must be created to restore customer access.
